{"type":"article","id":8637,"title":"香港天主教主教夏志诚到达现场希望和警方谈判，佐敦两人被捕一人不知生死","uid":14394,"topics":[17],"contents":"<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/eL8g9ap.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eL8g9ap.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/eL8g9ap.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/f0mO6YM.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/f0mO6YM.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/f0mO6YM.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/LlnZ2AK.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LlnZ2AK.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/LlnZ2AK.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n刚刚香港主教，民主派议员和美国众议院的一名议员去现场要求和警察对话，结果被警察喝骂赶走。<br>\n<br>\n辗转多地后终于有一名警察出来对话，不过毫无效果。<br>\n<br>\n另外佐敦发生警民冲突，混乱中两人被警察控制，其中一人倒卧在地不知生死，没有医护人员救护。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/U68D4fg.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/U68D4fg.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/U68D4fg.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-11-17","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":0}